Miss Mjadzelics had a two year on-off relationship with the rock star from 2006 and as time went on, Watkins revealed his sordid fantasies.

In August 2008, after receiving emails from the singer describing sex with an 11-year-old girl and suggestive photographs of a three-year-old, she went to police.

She told the Sunday People: 'I’m absolutely sure Ian wouldn’t have stopped at abuse.

'He wanted to rape and kill children. He wanted to rape newborns.

'He even wanted to get me pregnant so he could rape our baby.'

The singer, a former boyfriend of BBC presenter Fearne Cotton and model Alexa Chung, also admitted to her he used his Lostprophets fame to turn young girls into ‘Superfans’ willing to allow him to abuse their children.

